<view class="page-shell with-sticky-cta" id="page-action-plan">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="section-kicker">行动计划</view>
    <view class="panel-title">把容易慌乱的时刻提前写好答案</view>
    <view class="panel-subtitle">先想清楚“什么时候容易出问题”，再写下“我准备怎么做”，提醒出现时会更容易执行。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <view class="section-kicker">常用模板</view>
        <view class="panel-title">先选一个常见场景</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="preset-grid">
      <view
        wx:for="{{planPresets}}"
        wx:key="id"
        wx:for-item="preset"
        class="preset-card {{selectedPresetId === preset.id ? 'preset-card-active' : ''}}"
        data-id="{{preset.id}}"
        bindtap="applyPreset"
      >
        <view class="preset-title">{{preset.title}}</view>
        <view class="preset-body">{{preset.trigger}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="field-group">
      <text class="field-label">触发场景</text>
      <input
        id="input-plan-title"
        class="input"
        placeholder="例如：当疲乏达到 5 分时"
        value="{{form.trigger}}"
        data-key="trigger"
        bindinput="onFieldChange"
      />
    </view>

    <view class="field-group">
      <text class="field-label">行动计划</text>
      <textarea
        id="input-plan-strategy"
        class="textarea"
        auto-height="true"
        placeholder="例如：先暂停活动，分段步行 15 分钟并补充温水，再继续观察"
        value="{{form.response}}"
        data-key="response"
        bindinput="onFieldChange"
      ></textarea>
    </view>

    <view class="field-group">
      <text class="field-label">提醒时间</text>
      <picker mode="time" value="{{form.reminderTime}}" bindchange="onTimeChange">
        <view class="picker-field">
          <text>{{form.reminderTime}}</text>
          <text class="field-hint">点击选择</text>
        </view>
      </picker>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <view class="section-kicker">我的计划</view>
        <view class="panel-title">已经保存的提醒</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card-list" style="margin-top: 18rpx;" wx:if="{{plans.length}}">
      <view wx:for="{{plans}}" wx:key="id" wx:for-item="plan" class="list-card">
        <view class="plan-head">
          <view class="tag-row">
            <view class="tag">{{plan.reminderTime}}</view>
            <view class="tag {{plan.active ? 'tag-soft' : 'tag-danger'}}">{{plan.active ? '已启用' : '已暂停'}}</view>
          </view>
          <switch checked="{{plan.active}}" data-id="{{plan.id}}" bindchange="togglePlan" color="#c86a3b" />
        </view>
        <view class="list-title">{{plan.trigger}}</view>
        <view class="list-body">{{plan.response}}</view>
        <view class="plan-hint">{{plan.active ? '提醒会在设定时间出现，帮助你把计划真正执行下去。' : '当前已暂停提醒，需要时重新打开即可。'}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{!plans.length}}" class="empty-state">
      <view class="empty-icon">策</view>
      <view class="empty-title">还没有行动计划</view>
      <view class="empty-desc">先从一个最常见的困难场景开始，写下你准备怎样应对。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <view class="section-kicker">放松支持</view>
        <view class="panel-title">适合配合计划执行的课程</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card-list" style="margin-top: 18rpx;">
      <view wx:for="{{mindfulnessCourses}}" wx:key="id" wx:for-item="course" class="timeline-card">
        <view class="tag">{{course.durationMinutes}} 分钟</view>
        <view class="timeline-title">{{course.title}}</view>
        <view class="timeline-body">{{course.summary}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <view class="section-kicker">沟通模板</view>
        <view class="panel-title">和家人或医生沟通时可直接复制</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card-list" style="margin-top: 18rpx;">
      <view
        wx:for="{{communicationTemplates}}"
        wx:key="index"
        wx:for-item="template"
        class="timeline-card tappable-card"
        data-content="{{template}}"
        bindtap="copyTemplate"
      >
        <view class="timeline-body">{{template}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="sticky-cta">
    <view class="sticky-hint">写得越具体，提醒出现时越容易马上照着做。</view>
    <button
      id="button-save-action-plan"
      class="action-btn {{!canSave ? 'action-btn-disabled' : ''}}"
      bindtap="savePlan"
      disabled="{{!canSave || saving}}"
    >
      {{saving ? '保存中...' : '保存行动计划'}}
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
